    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you know you\u2019re getting a reliable car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures! It runs smooth and looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
